trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry"> </xref> objekter.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry> objects specify access rights for specific key containers.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry>objekter Angi tilgangsrettigheter for bestemte key beholdere.</xref:System.Security.Permissions.KeyContainerPermissionAccessEntry>
